 as one of the 50 funniest acts in British comedy.<p>

<it><link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../244/6206244.xml">
Olivia Joules and The Overactive Imagination</link></it>, a spoof on the spy genre, was published in 2004. </p>
<p>

The <reporter wordnetid="110521662" confidence="0.8">
