<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../985/172985.xml">
<it>The Daily Telegraph''</it></link></newspaper>
 in 1997 and 1998. In 2005, she resumed her Bridget Jones column at the Independent.  Bridget becomes pregnant and has a baby in this series, but love and commitment remain elusive. </p>
<p>

In her early years, she attended <school wordnetid="108276720" confidence="0.8">
<educational_institution wordnetid="108276342" confidence="0.8">
<institution wordnetid="108053576" confidence="0.8">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../932/4865932.xml">
Wakefield Girls High School</link></institution>
</educational_institution>
</school>
