Wakefield, England</link>. Fielding graduated from <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../374/128374.xml">
St. Anne's College</link>, <university wordnetid="108286163" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../797/31797.xml">
University of Oxford</link></university>
