<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../317/3555317.xml">
The Late, Late Breakfast Show</link></series>
</it> in the mid-1980s,<ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%221%22])">1</ref> before writing her first novel, <it>Cause Celeb</it>. She was for a time the girlfriend of screenwriter <film_director wordnetid="110088200" confidence="0.9173553029164789">
