In February 2004, she gave birth to her first child, a boy named Dashiell Michael, with longtime boyfriend <physical_entity wordnetid="100001930" confidence="0.8">
<communicator wordnetid="109610660" confidence="0.8">
<person wordnetid="100007846" confidence="0.8">
